Description: tiny Perl extension to generate cryptographically-secure random bytes.
 Bytes::Random::Secure::Tiny provides random bytes from a
 cryptographically secure random number generator (ISAAC), seeded from
 strong entropy sources on a wide variety of platforms. It does so
 without external dependencies (except on Windows), and has a minimal
 but useful user interface patterned after the module
 Bytes::Random::Secure.
